-- Author Sharma says U.S. Could Be 'Breakout Nation' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-04-09T21:26:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-09/author-sharma-says-u-s-could-be-breakout-nation-audio-.html
     April 9 (Bloomberg) - Ruchir Sharma, managing director and 
portfolio manager at Morgan Stanley Investment Management, 
discusses the big themes in the epilogue to the new edition of 
his book, "Breakout Nations: In Pursuit of the Next Economic 
Miracles" including his thesis that if the U.S. deals with its 
debt it could be one of the next "breakout nations."  Sharma 
spoke with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie Quinn on 
Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 17:54
 